WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:01.635
All right, good morning family.

00:00:01.635 --> 00:00:23.228
I have an urgency in my spirit right now to pray, so I’m just going to jump right into it and intercede.

00:00:23.228 --> 00:00:32.552
There are some things happening and I have an alert.

00:00:32.552 --> 00:03:06.899
When I get these, I’m just letting you all come in with me to pray over the election in Pennsylvania right now and the corruption I've seen.

00:03:06.899 --> 00:03:17.439
Diana, you can just jump right in.

00:03:17.439 --> 00:03:22.590
I’m going to pray in the spirit as I pray.

00:03:22.590 --> 00:05:27.857
If you may not understand it, it’s the baptism of the Holy Spirit.

00:05:45.528 --> 00:05:48.898
I don’t have time to explain it today, but we’ll have more time later.

00:05:48.898 --> 00:05:59.759
Holy Spirit, we flow for what you have for us now.

00:06:03.874 --> 00:06:05.646
We yield ourselves to you.

00:06:05.646 --> 00:06:11.803
Father, we thank you.

00:06:11.803 --> 00:06:50.120
We're not moved by emotion; we're moved by what the spirit says.

00:06:50.120 --> 00:07:32.089
Filled with and controlled by the Holy Ghost now, pray through us even more, Holy Spirit, as we yield ourselves to move.

00:07:33.382 --> 00:07:38.273
We pray for the hidden things.

00:07:40.434 --> 00:07:49.230
We come in boldly and we pray for the hidden things.

00:07:54.333 --> 00:08:27.266
In the stillness of the night, we uncover those things by angelic manifestation right now.

00:08:51.135 --> 00:09:45.430
In the stillness of the night, we uncover those things.

00:09:46.853 --> 00:10:12.512
We see the trucks; we see the ballots.

00:10:12.512 --> 00:11:42.160
I see you in the spirit and I uncover you in the name of Jesus.

00:11:43.155 --> 00:12:02.790
We send the angels now in Jesus' name for manifestation of this war and the corruption.

00:12:22.730 --> 00:12:46.187
We call for the corruption to be found out in Jesus' name.

00:12:46.187 --> 00:12:59.290
Pennsylvania, you will not do this, nor Virginia.

00:13:02.751 --> 00:13:06.060
We rise up in prayer.

00:13:18.852 --> 00:13:19.186
We take it.

00:13:19.186 --> 00:13:59.343
As they make their move, we thank you, Lord, that the plans of the enemy are foiled.

00:13:59.343 --> 00:14:15.050
It's not enough; they underestimated.

00:14:15.050 --> 00:14:29.710
Their plans are of the wicked and their minds are reprobate.

00:14:29.710 --> 00:15:55.380
We call forth the mind to be healed over the reprobate mind.

00:15:55.380 --> 00:17:42.549
We pray over it, Father, right now in the name of Jesus.

00:18:02.627 --> 00:18:29.894
This demonic thinking, we bind that, Father, for you said we wrestle not against flesh and blood, but against principalities, powers, and spiritual wickedness in high places.

00:19:06.613 --> 00:19:12.089
Father, we take authority over those devils right now in the name of Jesus, over that reprobate mind.

00:19:17.070 --> 00:19:18.729
We render you completely helpless now.

00:19:18.729 --> 00:19:24.680
We're going to Texas now.

00:19:24.680 --> 00:19:51.840
We're in Houston, for it will be decided in Houston, Lord, by each county.

00:19:51.840 --> 00:20:04.799
over Cruz, we pray over you in the name of Jesus.

00:20:04.799 --> 00:20:52.382
Over Austin, Texas; over Austin, you've gone predominantly liberal and we will not have this.

00:21:11.559 --> 00:21:18.856
We turn it now.

00:21:18.856 --> 00:21:39.799
Over Dallas, Fort Worth, and Arlington; over Helotes, San Antonio.

00:21:39.799 --> 00:22:53.720
Jesus, we're not moved by what we see or what we feel; we're moved by what the word says, and we have the victory in the name of Jesus.

00:22:53.720 --> 00:23:04.909
Now we're going to Atlanta, Georgia.

00:23:30.120 --> 00:23:31.800
We take authority over the spirit of racism in Jesus' name.

00:23:31.800 --> 00:24:06.795
We bind that spirit.

00:24:06.795 --> 00:24:36.060
You're a foul stench; get out of here in the name of Jesus.

00:24:36.060 --> 00:24:59.042
Racism will not do this.

00:24:59.042 --> 00:25:21.069
Father, we thank you for a mending of the hearts.

00:25:23.023 --> 00:25:39.952
There's great hurt in the hearts from generation to generation.

00:25:39.952 --> 00:26:01.925
We minister to the African-Americans in the spirit.

00:26:01.925 --> 00:26:28.966
We pray peace and call comfort over their hearts.

00:26:28.966 --> 00:26:43.485
We call for peace and restoration.

00:26:43.485 --> 00:27:02.451
Everything that was stolen, Father, for the cankerworm has been found.

00:27:02.451 --> 00:27:16.159
We call out that cankerworm and say restoration of double in Jesus' name.

00:27:16.159 --> 00:27:30.123
Restoration of double in the name of Jesus to make things right.

00:27:30.123 --> 00:27:40.164
This will happen in the spirit.

00:27:44.183 --> 00:28:05.369
The hearts in the Deep South; the roots of heart to be heard.

00:28:05.369 --> 00:28:11.653
Is anyone listening to me?

00:28:11.653 --> 00:28:21.529
All the way through Chicago.

00:28:44.320 --> 00:29:11.030
Father, only you can fix this, Lord, by your grace, your mercy, the anointing, and the glory.

00:29:12.005 --> 00:29:27.510
The glory breaks down the walls of pain, hurt, and bitterness.

00:29:27.510 --> 00:29:48.148
A wave of glory on this nation from coast to coast.

00:30:00.960 --> 00:30:06.816
I call for a restoration over the Hispanic community, the Latinos.

00:30:13.017 --> 00:30:21.480
Father, we pray for a revival over the Hispanic community.

00:30:21.940 --> 00:30:43.760
Father, we call forth the fire of God to visit their churches and the people.

00:30:43.760 --> 00:31:57.308
Over the Cubans, over the Puerto Ricans, we call forth a supernatural visitation and manifestation of the glory.

00:31:57.308 --> 00:32:13.451
They have been lied to by so many.

00:32:13.451 --> 00:32:43.399
I thank you, Father, for great discernment, not just hearing what we want to hear, but hearing what you say.

00:32:43.399 --> 00:32:54.450
We're not being lied to by the enemy.

00:32:54.450 --> 00:33:00.565
Lord, you're showing me so much.

00:33:00.565 --> 00:33:17.146
We speak for the Senate to be red.

00:33:19.426 --> 00:33:28.976
The embarrassment that they do not want to face, they are trying to cover up out of corruption.

00:33:28.976 --> 00:33:33.759
It's in these certain counties.

00:33:33.759 --> 00:34:56.240
I'm looking at individual corruption in the counties, swaying certain counties to go blue, trying to control the vote by a margin, a thin line of maybe 20,000 votes placed in strategic places so it's not detectable.

00:35:48.560 --> 00:35:48.865
Father, let all hidden things be revealed.

00:35:48.865 --> 00:35:59.275
We wake up the Boomers in every culture, tribe, and tongue.

00:36:05.435 --> 00:36:37.920
We wake up the Boomers, the elderly generation, for they will carry this one more time.

00:36:37.920 --> 00:37:15.486
Lord said, 'I only need one more time,' for there will be a beginning of a quick work.

00:37:19.275 --> 00:37:29.360
The manifestations of my glory will come in a wave you've never seen before—a great red wave.

00:37:30.933 --> 00:37:40.554
They underestimated it, for they have a reprobate mind.

00:37:42.920 --> 00:38:02.404
They are not thinking with the mind of Christ; they think with a demonic mind.

00:38:02.404 --> 00:38:09.480
Their math is off.

00:38:22.427 --> 00:38:27.013
There's a spirit of confusion in their camp and it rests heavily on them.

00:38:27.013 --> 00:38:48.200
As they do corruption, the spirit of confusion is heavy in the camp—bickering and strife among them.

00:38:48.200 --> 00:39:02.311
Where there is strife, there is confusion and every evil work.

00:39:02.311 --> 00:39:07.893
It's infiltrating their camps right now.

00:39:10.836 --> 00:39:26.147
The enemy is not the people; they have yielded themselves over to a demonic spirit.

00:39:26.147 --> 00:39:43.143
You're not wrestling against people; this is an antichrist spirit opposing my word.

00:39:43.143 --> 00:40:21.215
We're praying for their salvation and that the blinders Satan has placed over the eyes of the unbeliever be taken off.

00:40:48.977 --> 00:40:56.880
We pray for unity and peace, and that they would see the errors in their ways.

00:40:56.880 --> 00:41:09.223
It's not blue against red; it's light against darkness.

00:41:09.223 --> 00:41:40.230
We call for their eyes to be enlightened, even tomorrow in the polling booth.

00:41:40.230 --> 00:42:18.329
Angels of the Lord, manifest and make war against those demonic spirits right now.

00:42:18.329 --> 00:43:16.751
Father, we thank you that even the counties in California are fed up.

00:43:16.751 --> 00:43:18.648
I see it.

00:43:18.648 --> 00:43:45.145
Even the ones that would want to sway to the far left are fed up with the taxes and the unfair treatment.

00:43:45.145 --> 00:44:53.990
I see even great Hollywood celebrities saying they're frustrated with the way this is going with Gavin Newsom.

00:44:53.990 --> 00:46:18.737
I call a red wave in Jesus' name, a turnout of red like they've never seen before, because they want hope and change.

00:46:18.737 --> 00:46:59.365
But the only one that will bring great change is you, through preaching righteousness and holiness, not a seeker-friendly gospel.

00:46:59.365 --> 00:47:10.320
Break the chains, Father.

00:47:10.320 --> 00:48:11.580
As we go into Nevada and Arizona, we pray for Kari Lake and the others, that they come out bolder and stronger with a backbone like a crowbar.

00:48:11.580 --> 00:48:36.868
We send angels in the nighttime when corruption tries to be at its greatest.

00:48:36.868 --> 00:48:51.000
We call for an uncovering and exposing of things.

00:48:51.000 --> 00:49:54.271
We call for uncorrupt police to show up and have the boldness to expose it, to abide by their oath and the stirring of a conscience inside of them to blow the whistle in the darkness.

00:49:54.271 --> 00:50:09.839
We pray for the postal workers; if there is corruption, let them be found out.

00:50:47.335 --> 00:50:58.280
If they try to bury or burn the ballots, let them be found in Jesus' name.

00:50:58.280 --> 00:51:33.320
You've shown me the corruption in these people, Father, but we call these things around right now.

00:51:48.861 --> 00:51:49.119
I saw the truck, and it was like an unmarked truck.

00:51:49.119 --> 00:51:59.280
But the Lord was saying to me, 'They undershot.

00:51:59.280 --> 00:52:16.177
' They were trying to be sneaky, but they undershot.

00:52:16.177 --> 00:52:18.740
They don't have enough time.

00:52:18.740 --> 00:52:24.729
Especially in that county—it’s Pennsylvania.

00:52:39.980 --> 00:52:40.280
I saw the number 23,000.

00:52:40.280 --> 00:53:02.259
Father, we take communion and thank you that all hidden things will be revealed.

00:53:02.259 --> 00:53:18.411
We see the red wave starting in Michigan, Minnesota, Illinois.

00:53:18.411 --> 00:53:56.750
I pray for a red wave in Jesus' name, an uncontainable wave of glory upon this land from sea to shining sea.

00:54:01.453 --> 00:54:12.575
I saw in the spirit a dark storm upon the East Coast.

00:54:12.575 --> 00:54:29.960
Out of this, I saw four beautiful white doves circling in figure-eights.

00:54:39.520 --> 00:54:48.549
The glory of the Lord was resting on four doves.

00:54:48.549 --> 00:55:00.720
It either means four years or four consecutive years.

00:55:00.720 --> 00:55:19.229
The storm was violent, but there was light in Goshen.

00:55:19.229 --> 00:55:38.309
I saw the house again, with the place being prepared.

00:55:38.309 --> 00:55:54.470
Psalms 91 and Psalms 23.

00:56:14.303 --> 00:56:18.244
He prepares a table before me in the presence of my enemies.

00:56:18.244 --> 00:56:42.352
Surely goodness and mercy follow us all the days of our life.

00:56:51.175 --> 00:56:54.079
We stand in the gap for America.

00:56:54.079 --> 00:57:03.510
Father, you have a great plan for America.

00:57:03.510 --> 00:57:05.386
One last push.

00:57:07.240 --> 00:57:13.020
A four-year window here before Jesus Christ comes.

00:57:13.020 --> 00:57:27.640
We need a revival beyond anything we can comprehend.

00:57:27.640 --> 00:57:35.160
I feel the presence of the Lord.

00:57:35.160 --> 00:57:48.080
Holy Spirit, invade these people in their homes.

00:57:48.080 --> 00:58:01.839
Father, you have one last call for America.

00:58:07.549 --> 00:58:14.745
We pray for your hand of judgment to be upon the wicked.

00:58:14.745 --> 00:58:24.680
Remove those that stand in the way of your great revival.

00:58:24.680 --> 00:58:37.229
One last call for a harvest.

00:58:37.229 --> 00:58:38.844
Four years.

00:58:39.599 --> 00:58:55.607
The Holy Spirit represents the glory that descended on Jesus like a dove.

00:58:56.949 --> 00:58:58.130
We invite you.

00:58:58.130 --> 00:59:01.927
Four years.

00:59:01.927 --> 00:59:14.533
You give America four more years for a supernatural harvest.

00:59:28.547 --> 00:59:38.605
I saw those doves go into solid light; they became one big light and it dispatched over all the glory.

00:59:38.605 --> 00:59:46.780
It's spreading over Texas, over Houston.

00:59:48.644 --> 01:00:04.160
The glory of the latter house will be greater than the former.

01:00:04.160 --> 01:00:19.335
Four years of the greater glory.

01:00:19.335 --> 01:00:30.109
This is what you've prayed for.

01:00:30.109 --> 01:00:40.130
It started from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

01:00:40.130 --> 01:01:10.079
First the blade, then the ear, then the full manifestation of the glory.

01:01:10.079 --> 01:01:19.889
This is your window.

01:01:23.022 --> 01:01:26.467
What will you do with the time I've given you?

01:01:26.467 --> 01:01:31.320
For my son's return is imminent.

01:01:36.663 --> 01:01:41.039
The sun is setting on this dispensation.

01:01:41.039 --> 01:01:50.240
It's time for you to soar.

01:01:50.240 --> 01:02:18.902
I saw the glory of the Lord flowing in each individual person as they come up higher to the throne.

01:02:18.902 --> 01:02:30.702
There's a special place prepared for each of you.

01:02:42.327 --> 01:02:43.574
It's by grace.

01:02:43.574 --> 01:03:07.207
It's a renewing of your mind.

01:03:07.207 --> 01:03:22.845
Change the way you think because it's been in reprobate thinking.

01:03:22.845 --> 01:03:32.489
You allowed the enemy to tell you that you're not good enough, but I've done it all.

01:03:32.489 --> 01:03:42.839
I see everyone sitting before the throne, resting.

01:03:42.839 --> 01:04:02.909
So you've got to take your place.

01:04:11.949 --> 01:04:13.099
He's coming soon.

01:04:13.099 --> 01:04:31.200
I'm going to give you one last call.

01:04:31.200 --> 01:04:49.380
Will you squander this time or will you march on and take the land with me?

01:04:49.380 --> 01:04:59.880
For the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few.

01:04:59.880 --> 01:05:07.618
Who will help me bring in my harvest?

01:05:07.618 --> 01:05:18.986
These are no longer last days; I'm giving you seconds.

01:05:18.986 --> 01:05:28.500
I am right at the door.

01:05:28.840 --> 01:05:37.080
It's time for you all to come up higher.

01:05:37.080 --> 01:05:50.239
Take the care out of the prayer and shake off the beggar's cloak.

01:05:50.239 --> 01:06:00.409
Like blind Bartimaeus had to throw off the beggar's cloak.

01:06:10.912 --> 01:06:16.924
In the spirit, you have to take off the old leper's cloak and come up higher.

01:06:16.924 --> 01:06:21.729
How do you see yourself?

01:06:21.729 --> 01:06:30.935
Bound and broken, or seated with me in the heavenlies?

01:06:38.768 --> 01:06:39.013
You can pluck like chickens or soar like eagles.

01:06:39.746 --> 01:06:51.044
You choose by renewing your mind and staying in prayer.

01:06:51.044 --> 01:06:58.947
I am standing at the door.

01:06:58.947 --> 01:07:04.960
He's coming through the door.

01:07:09.050 --> 01:07:09.846
It's no longer days; it's seconds.

01:07:09.846 --> 01:07:14.548
He's given us a window.

01:07:28.515 --> 01:07:29.180
I extended the grace.

01:07:29.180 --> 01:07:48.470
I've given you a little window, a fraction, and the glorious church will rise out of it.

01:07:48.470 --> 01:07:55.320
It's about the next Shemitah cycle.

01:07:55.320 --> 01:08:17.502
If you don't know what the Shemitah is, go read Rabbi Jonathan Cahn's book on the Shemitah.

01:08:26.528 --> 01:08:30.810
When the next Shemitah cycle ends in 2028, this is a great window.

01:08:30.810 --> 01:08:37.093
What will you do with that timeframe?

01:08:42.155 --> 01:08:45.770
It has everything to do with the Shemitah cycle.

01:08:45.770 --> 01:09:01.040
Father, we thank you for your body that was broken for us.

01:09:06.679 --> 01:09:22.520
We dedicate our lives to come up higher and shake off the beggar's cloak.

01:09:22.520 --> 01:09:37.719
We are sons and daughters of the Most High God.

01:09:51.469 --> 01:09:51.880
We will walk in victory and light.

01:09:51.880 --> 01:10:08.486
Let that light shine through us today.

01:10:08.486 --> 01:10:15.393
Father, we thank you for the blood.

01:10:18.871 --> 01:10:28.900
I thank you, Lord, that our eyes are being flooded with light.

01:10:28.900 --> 01:10:50.557
We plead the blood over America, Asia, Africa, Russia, and South America.

01:11:04.540 --> 01:11:06.870
It's time.

01:11:06.880 --> 01:11:37.813
I saw all God's children sitting by his throne.

01:11:37.813 --> 01:11:47.580
All different cultures, no race, no color.

01:11:47.580 --> 01:12:32.496
He doesn't see through the eyes of stupidity; he sees everyone as one.

01:13:04.052 --> 01:13:12.338
The devil has tried so hard to blind people with race, gender, and age.

01:13:42.086 --> 01:13:42.343
What will we do before the next Shemitah cycle in 2028?

01:13:42.343 --> 01:13:45.417
He's coming quick.

01:13:45.417 --> 01:14:09.248
If you haven't asked him into your heart, there are no more delays.

01:14:09.248 --> 01:14:36.587
Say a simple prayer: 'Father, forgive me of my sins.

01:14:36.587 --> 01:14:47.020
Write my name in the Lamb's Book of Life.

01:14:57.738 --> 01:14:58.076
I believe you're the Son of God.

01:14:58.076 --> 01:15:10.116
' Get baptized, find a church, stop sinning, and get in the Word every day.

01:15:10.733 --> 01:15:29.411
You have the Great Commission to lay hands on the sick, cast out devils, and raise the dead.

01:15:29.411 --> 01:15:39.820
Do something big before the next Shemitah cycle.

01:15:54.000 --> 01:15:54.627
I'm going to keep doing these prayer videos.

01:15:54.627 --> 01:16:09.120
We're going to have good results in Jesus' name.

01:16:09.120 --> 01:16:14.400
We plowed like an icebreaker today.

01:16:14.400 --> 01:16:25.093
I'm never in a hurry when the presence is thick.

01:16:25.093 --> 01:16:37.320
Why worry about things that don't count for eternity?

01:16:37.320 --> 01:16:39.396
Everything's about eternity.

01:16:39.396 --> 01:17:13.548
Some people focusing on earthly things will realize how foolish they were.

01:17:19.053 --> 01:17:39.880
I don't talk about the Thousand Years because I don't have scripture to back up the specific things I've seen, but it's beautiful.

01:17:39.880 --> 01:17:41.771
Everything's restored.

01:17:46.818 --> 01:17:47.022
No smog, no pollution.

01:17:47.022 --> 01:17:51.160
Vegetables the size of beachballs.

01:17:59.600 --> 01:17:59.920
We'll be in a glorified body.

01:17:59.920 --> 01:18:08.291
I'm taking these doTERRA peppermint beads.

01:18:08.291 --> 01:18:16.256
They help a lot.

01:18:18.581 --> 01:18:21.800
I was focusing on those doves.

01:18:27.845 --> 01:18:31.548
The glory went out as they spread over the earth.

01:18:32.084 --> 01:18:41.724
I saw a fire going around the middle of the earth.

01:18:51.685 --> 01:18:51.988
The Holy Spirit fire spreading glory around the whole earth.

01:18:51.988 --> 01:18:57.600
I believe each dove represents four years.

01:19:02.470 --> 01:19:04.530
Jesus is standing at the door.

01:19:04.530 --> 01:19:11.418
What will you do with that window?

01:19:11.418 --> 01:19:16.491
Subscribe and like the video.

01:19:16.491 --> 01:19:21.280
We will pray again tomorrow.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.250
We're believing this thing is over today and will be called quickly in Jesus' name.

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.400
God bless you all.
